    <div class="container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h2 class="fw-bold">What Our Members Say</h2>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Hear from farmers and energy providers who are part of our community</p>
        </div>

        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img src="~/images/sunrisefarm.jpg" alt="Testimonial" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="60" height="60">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Thabo Nkosi</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Organic Farmer, Limpopo</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-0">"Since implementing solar irrigation from a provider I found on this platform, I've reduced my operational costs by 40% and improved my crop yield significantly."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img src="~/images/greenvalleyfarm.jpg" alt="Testimonial" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="60" height="60">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Lerato Molefe</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Solar Solutions Provider, Gauteng</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-0">"This platform has connected us with farmers who are truly committed to sustainability. We've expanded our client base and made a real impact in rural communities."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4 mb-4">
                <div class="card h-100 border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-4">
                            <img src="~/images/highlandfarm.jpg" alt="Testimonial" class="rounded-circle me-3" width="60" height="60">
                            <div>
                                <h5 class="mb-0">Daniel van der Merwe</h5>
                                <p class="text-muted mb-0">Livestock Farmer, Western Cape</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <p class="mb-0">"The biogas system I implemented based on advice from this community has turned my waste management problem into an energy solution. It's a game-changer for my farm."</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>